                <ul>
                    <li>Master passive voice structure (be + past participle)</li>
                    <li>Practice converting active sentences to passive voice</li>
                    <li>Use passive voice in natural conversation</li>
                    <li>Apply passive voice in cultural and global contexts</li>
                    <li>Develop confidence in asking and answering questions using passive voice</li>
