                <div class="question">
                    <div class="question-number">Question 1:</div>
                    <p><strong>Teacher asks:</strong> "What languages are spoken in your country?"</p>
                    <button class="answer-btn" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">Sample Answer</button>
                    <div class="answer"><strong>Sample response:</strong> "Japanese is spoken by most people in Japan, but English is also taught in schools and is used in international business."</div>
