                <div class="question">
                    <div class="question-number">Question 2:</div>
                    <p><strong>Teacher asks:</strong> "How is traditional Japanese food prepared?"</p>
                    <button class="answer-btn" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">Sample Answer</button>
                    <div class="answer"><strong>Sample response:</strong> "Traditional Japanese food is prepared with fresh ingredients and is often served with rice. Sushi is made by skilled chefs and sashimi is cut very precisely."</div>
                </div>

                <div class="question">
                    <div class="question-number">Question 3:</div>
                    <p><strong>Teacher asks:</strong> "What festivals are celebrated in Japan during spring?"</p>
                    <button class="answer-btn" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">Sample Answer</button>
                    <div class="answer"><strong>Sample response:</strong> "Cherry blossom festivals are celebrated throughout Japan in spring. Hanami parties are organized by families and friends under the blooming trees."</div>
                </div>

                <div class="question">
                    <div class="question-number">Question 4:</div>
                    <p><strong>Teacher asks:</strong> "How are Japanese companies known internationally?"</p>
                    <button class="answer-btn" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">Sample Answer</button>
                    <div class="answer"><strong>Sample response:</strong> "Japanese companies are known for their quality products and innovation. Cars are manufactured by companies like Toyota and Honda, and electronics are produced by Sony and Panasonic."</div>
                </div>

                <div class="question">
                    <div class="question-number">Question 5:</div>
                    <p><strong>Teacher asks:</strong> "What changes have been made to Japanese society in recent decades?"</p>
                    <button class="answer-btn" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">Sample Answer</button>
                    <div class="answer"><strong>Sample response:</strong> "Many changes have been made to Japanese society. Technology has been integrated into daily life, and more opportunities have been created for women in the workplace."</div>
                </div>
