                <h3>üìù What We Learned Today</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Passive Voice Structure:</strong> Subject + be + past participle + (by + agent)</li>
                    <li><strong>Usage:</strong> Focus on the action or result rather than who performs the action</li>
                    <li><strong>Cultural Application:</strong> Describing traditions, innovations, and cultural practices</li>
                    <li><strong>Conversation Practice:</strong> Asking and answering questions naturally</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="objectives">
                <h3>üè† Homework Suggestion</h3>
                <p>Practice describing your daily routine using passive voice. For example: "Breakfast is eaten at 7 AM," "The news is watched every morning," "Messages are sent to friends throughout the day."</p>
